<h1>About StockRequester</h1>

<p>
    StockRequester is a web-based inventory management system designed to streamline the process of 
    transferring stock between different company locations.<br />
    It provides a simple, intuitive interface for managing stock movements.
</p>

<p>
    Built using ASP.NET MVC, StockRequester leverages modern web technologies to provide 
    a secure platform for your inventory management needs.
</p>

<p>
    Developed by <a href="https://github.com/SamsRepos" target="_blank">Sam Burrows</a>, 
    a software development engineer with a BSc with First Class Honours in Computer Games Technology 
    from the University of Abertay.
</p>

